l my heart and want everything for you and more . Bless this world with your joyful presence, as you share your gifts in this world.', 10332, 0), (119983, 'I heard that I am your biggest disappointment,yet, in my heart, I know and feel that I am the greatest version of myself ever and celebrate myself each and every day', 10332, 0), (119984, 'NOIT''S NO ONE''S FAULTBack then, what I really resented was my own powerless self. my tiny little self. and my tiny little heart.too small to hold all that emotion, so it had to shift the blame onto someone else.but now I''m grown. I''VE COME FOR YOU. I''LL HOLD IT ALL.Kuki Urie', 2499, 0), (119985, 'Give your all in the Here and Now , with all of your heart', 10332, 0), (119986, 'Scared but still dare to follow my heart', 16535, 0), (119987, 'Where could I call home? Only in my heart.', 2878, 0), (119988, 'Walking and looking at the stars with you, wondering what our futures holds. treasures kept safe in our hearts to cherish forever. I miss those days', 16535, 0), (119989, 'Scary to be vulnerable, to open your heart but, oh, the out of this world feeling as you savor the pleasure!', 10332, 0), (119990, 'It is in opposing the world’s lies that we impose truth in our hearts.', 4397, 0), (119991, 'It is better to have a warm than cold heart.', 2878, 0), (119992, 'The heart is the only sacred home.', 2878, 0), (119993, 'Nothing can contain the limitless spirit of a boundless heart.', 5043, 0), (119994, 'When the tidal waves wildly behavingMy bare feet on the shore busy savingThe calm warmth leaking out of the sandTo let my heart feel peacefully tanned!', 2760, 0), (119995, 'Pink! My color! My love!', 23290, 0), (119996, 'my heart woke me crying last nighthow can i help i beggedmy heart said write the book', 694, 0), (119997, 'Destiny isn''t a path any cat follows blindly. It is always a matter of choice, and sometimes the heart speaks loudest. Listen to your heart, because that''s where your true destiny lies.', 2082, 0), (11999